headline: Xcel Energy Second Quarter 2025 Earnings Conference Call
summary: MINNEAPOLIS, July 01, 2025--On Thursday, July 31, 2025, Xcel Energy (NASDAQ: XEL) will host a conference call to review second quarter 2025 financial results. The earnings report will be released prior to the market open on the same date.
